summary: This document is a declaration by LaTisha R. Hough, a Legal Process Manager/Paralegal at TD Ameritrade, certifying the authenticity of certain business records. It outlines her qualifications and the procedures followed in maintaining these records, affirming their accuracy and reliability.

persons.name: LaTisha R. Hough
persons.context: LaTisha R. Hough certifies the authenticity of business records from TD Ameritrade, where she is employed.

persons.name: Nicole Neawin
persons.context: Nicole Neawin is mentioned as the notary public who witnessed the declaration by LaTisha R. Hough.

keyFacts: LaTisha R. Hough is employed by TD Ameritrade as a Legal Process Manager / Paralegal.
The declaration certifies that the attached documents are true copies of records made in the course of regular business activity.
The declaration was executed on October 1, 2019.
Nicole Neawin is the notary public who witnessed the declaration.
